letter-spacing property 
justify-content property 
align-items property 

use a bold class in cases where there are lots of bold elements
span element : used to style specific portions of text

create dividers with classes and target elements in them with the structure 
  .divider-class element { property }

<div class="divider medium"></div>
  - .divider and .medium selectors defined separately in css file but both apply to this div

:not pseudo-selector can selects all elements that do not match given css rule
div:not(#example) {
  color: red;
}
  - all div elements without an id of example; 
